<Layout title="Brisbane Property Settlement When the Buyer Is Interstate or Overseas 2026: Remote Handover Logistics | Daniel Gierach Property" description="What changes for Queensland sellers when the buyer cannot attend settlement in person. Key handover, pre-settlement inspection, communication and the practical risks of selling to a remote buyer." schema={faqSchema}>

<article style="background:var(--color-surface-0);min-height:100vh;">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div style="background:#e6d9bd;padding:8rem 0 3rem;">
    <div class="max-w-[780px] mx-auto px-8">
